s of the image, Jain demonstrates how these new aesthetic forms entail a simultaneously religious and political retooling of the “infrastructures of the sensible.”  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aAestheticsxReligious aspects. 0aArt and popular culturezIndia. 0aArt and religionzIndiaxHistoryy21st century. 0aArt and societyzIndiaxHistoryy21st century. 0aCommercial artzIndia. 0aGods in art. 0aIdols and images in art. 0aLarge-scale sculpturezIndiay21st centuryxThemes, motives. 0aReligion and culturezIndia. 7aART / Sculpture & Installation.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDuke University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311074331908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2021z9783110753783oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2021 Englishz978311075403208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781478012887?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478012887423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781478012887/original  a978-3-11-074331-9  Duke University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075403-2  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2021 Englishb2021  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DADb2021  aZDB-23-DGGb2021